            <span id="login-text" class="block text-3xl text-amber-50 border-2 border-fuchsia-500 p-4 bg-fuchsia-900 rounded hover:bg-fuchsia-500 hover:border-fuchsia-300 hover:text-fuchsia-950">Iniciar sesiÃ³n</span>
